UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''"Warchief Vol''''jin." Does it sound absurd to you, $c? I, for one, certainly won''''t be taking orders from a troll.$b$b\\nBut, he put this little coalition together, and won the day. He''''s also proven to be impossible to kill - I admire that.$b$b\\nTime to test what he''''s made of...''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=77365;
