UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''<An inscription on the hilt reads:>\\n\\n"Here Vindicator Torvath fell in battle to end the rage of the ancients.\\n\\n May the light shine upon this grove that he so valiantly fought to protect and may it forever bring peace upon its denizens."''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=81812;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''You look like an able fisherman, do you think you can help us out?\\n\\nWe have established a small garrison nearby, but we are finding it difficult to feed our troops. Any fishing advice you could give us would really help.''', `FemaleText`='''You look like an able fisherman, do you think you can help us out?\\n\\nWe have established a small garrison nearby, but we are finding it difficult to feed our troops. Any fishing advice you could give us would really help.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID` IN (81873, 85994);
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Get back to work!''', `SoundID`=52698, `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=81924;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''The essence font allows you to break down weapons and armor into enchanting materials.  The item is PERMANENTLY destroyed.\\n\\nDo you wish to continue?''', `FemaleText`='''The essence font allows you to break down weapons and armor into enchanting materials.  The item is PERMANENTLY destroyed.\\n\\nDo you wish to continue?''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=82176;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''Have you seen any of the hidden artifacts?$B$BYou can find fragments all throughout Ashran. I hear killing the creatures in this the outskirts off of the Road of Glory has uncovered some recently. $B$BYou can give me any you find, and I''''ll distribute them to those who need them.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=82999;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''I''''m well aware that the fish are more plentiful in the upper pools. However, a real professional knows that the big ones prefer a spot with a little more cover. \\n\\nJust wait until Roluna sees what I can land down here in the weeds!''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83103;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''A trader with an empty cart, such a sad sight, no? \\n\\nIf only my partner Daruun would make up his mind so we could be on our way.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83118;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''It''''s a lovely plant, yes? What color would be best suited for Shattrath''''s markets? \\n\\nDoes anyone even buy plants these days?''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83119;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Together, we have crushed the slavers and brought upon them swift destruction. They who have taken everything from me. \\n\\nBut, I have one last thing to give. To be a part of something greater... I''''d forgotten what that feels like.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83167;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''In my profession I have learned that the nature of crystals is very much like that of the Draenei people. \\n\\nThe core material has amazing potential, but begins as rough and heavily flawed. It is only through careful shaping and nurturing that its potential can truly be reached. \\n\\nOnly then can it show its magnificent beauty and wondrous clarity.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83192;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''Oh, that? I may have hitched a ride through your garrison portal. \\n\\nThey should probably guard those things better, come to think of it.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83336;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''The skies hold untold wonders, waiting to be discovered. Our researchers study the stars and beyond over at the observatory. \\n\\nIf you have time, traveler, I would recommend paying it a visit.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83346;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''The ranchers of Embaari raise elekk and talbuk to supply Shattrath, as well as many of the smaller draenei villages. \\n\\nIf you wish to review the livestock, you can find their ranches along the outskirts of the village.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83347;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''What little supplies we had upon arrival are quickly being used up for the needs of the refugees. \\n\\nI hope we are able to leave here soon, lest we become stranded in Auchindoun just like them.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83691;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Take care, the demons can strike again at any moment. It seems the Shadow Council will stop at nothing to breach the gates of Auchindoun.\\n\\nWe must remain vigilant!''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83728;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''Some of the larger demons can tear through our ballistae relatively quickly. \\n\\nIf I can''''t produce them more rapidly than they get destroyed, then there may be no stopping the Shadow Council.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83763;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''I understand that our relationship with the Draenei has been through some trying times, but right now, these soldiers need my help. \\n\\nWe need to stick together if we all wish to defeat the Shadow Council.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83776;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''These pilgrims gather from all over Draenor to hear the wisdom of the spirits interred at Auchindoun. \\n\\nFor the draenei people, such wisdom comes with great reward.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83796;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''The skirmishes with the Shadow Council have left many travelers stranded in Auchindoun. \\n\\nUnless the tide of battle turns, it is likely we will never leave this place.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83797;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''These great defense crystals are just one of the myriad uses for the crystals in the Jorune mine. \\n\\nIt is a pity that the Shadow Council forces us to use them only for instruments of war.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83804;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Tressia was a good solider, but when the venom took its hold on her, she left me no choice. \\n\\nI hope we wipe every member of the Shadow Council from the face of Draenor. Our people deserve better than to end up like this.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83823;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''So far, none of our medicines have had any effect on the spiders'''' poison. \\n\\nWe must gather more specimens before we can concoct an effective antidote.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=83870;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''In order to successfully train a fey dragon, one must keep them well fed and rested. A restless dragon tends to be less than receptive to orders.\\n\\nPlease do not disturb them.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=84047;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Here is where we train the young fey darters to follow commands. \\n\\nThough their antics may seem silly, the discipline they learn now is imperative if we ever wish them to take a rider.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=84049;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''Brighteye is one of the smartest fey dragons we''''ve trained at the Draakorium. He loves doing tricks for visitors!\\n\\nWhy don''''t you see if Brighteye can do a trick for you?''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=84064;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''DISCLAIMER:\\n\\nThe Steamwheedle Preservation Society will not be held liable for any accidental deaths, dismemberments or mutilations involved with rocket-propelled ascensions.\\n\\nMisti Zingwozzer,\\nLegal Department, Steamwheedle Preservation Society''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=84220;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Check it out here, got the best seats in the house!\\n\\nDid you come here to watch some fights, too?''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=84251;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''Did the boss send you?\\n\\nLook, if he asks, just tell him I''''m doing some underwater excavation.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=84529;
