UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''She''''s nothing now, a twisted soul chained to our world.  My sister was so sweet, so loving, so young... The Shadowmoon did this!  Twisted her by some foul magic! They left her walking the world as a shadow, crying out in eternal torment.\\n\\nI couldn''''t.  I can''''t.  I cannot end her pain.  I cannot be the one to relive her pain.\\n\\nRelease her spirit.  Put her to rest.  I cannot bear seeing her like this.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=84628;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''So you''''ve done it?  Well, then.  Be gone and leave me to my mourning.\\n\\nSo young... she was so young...''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=84629;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''|TInterface\\\\Icons\\\\sha_ability_rogue_bloodyeye.blp:32|t$b\\n|cFFFF0000|Hspell:167410|h[Khadgar''''s Watch]|h|r reverses time!''', `FemaleText`='''|TInterface\\\\Icons\\\\sha_ability_rogue_bloodyeye.blp:32|t$b\\n|cFFFF0000|Hspell:167410|h[Khadgar''''s Watch]|h|r reverses time!''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=85114;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''To prove yourself worthy of the wolf, you must first test your strength and tenacity. \\n\\nTo do this, you must gather a heavy stone from the quarry and bear it on your back into the lands of your enemy. Once you have cut your way through their ranks, place the stone in a place of prominence, and set upon it a trophy of your foe.\\n\\nOnly then, when your strength is displayed for all to see, can you hope to claim the wolf as your subject.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=85330;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Once your display of strength is set for all to see, you must claim your wolf.\\n\\nGo to their hunting grounds. There you must find the largest wolf in the pack, and subdue it in the presence of its kin. You will likely be eaten alive, but if you survive the ordeal, the wolf will answer to you as its master.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=85331;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''It is not enough that the wolf regard you as its master. To ready your wolf for riding, you must break its will completely.\\n\\nOnce you have subdued your wolf, you will mount it and ride it to the top of the tallest peak in Nagrand. If your wolf is willful, it will throw you to your death on the mountain slopes. \\n\\nIf you survive to the peak, the will of your wolf will be broken. \\n\\nThen, you can call yourself "Wolfrider".''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=85332;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''This Warsong orc looks to have died trying to carry a giant stone through the Gorian outpost. \\n\\nThere''''s no clear indication of where he was taking the stone, but it obviously didn''''t help him in combat.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=85395;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Amongst many scribbled entries of the trials of a pirate''''s life and a surprising amount of different uses for barnacles, you find an entry of note:\\n\\n"''''Tis been a week since that cursed bird made off with the keys to my chest. He keeps flyin'''' by, as if he be tauntin'''' me, but I can''''t seem to to catch him on the wing. \\n\\nThat good for nothin'''' squab can''''t fly forever. I''''ll just wait here ''''till he goes aground."''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=85533;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''Fellworth got our group lost by finding a "shortcut" through the hollow and now my boots are full of slime and mud!\\n\\nI think I will be charge of the map from now on.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=85659;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''It bein'''' just my luck, mon! I be findin'''' da best fishin'''' spot down ''''ere, but only after da elementals and da ogres broke up all my gear. \\n\\nNow I''''m needin'''' a new rod, reel, and da special voodoo lure so I can land da big ones hidin'''' in da weeds.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=85674;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Switching the building will cost 5,000 gold.\\n\\nAre you sure?''', `FemaleText`='''Switching the building will cost 5,000 gold.\\n\\nAre you sure?''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=85688;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Tommy Joe, last time you took a bath \\nwas before the Cataclysm.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=86085;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Greetings, and thank you for helping to test the Warlords of Draenor Beta! \\n\\nI can teleport you directly into a number of raid or dungeon instances that are currently open for testing. This is just a teleport, not a match-making service, so I hope you have a party ready to tackle the challenges waiting inside. If not, you might want to check out our new Group Finder feature to find some allies.\\n\\nMake sure you have selected the difficulty you want to test before teleporting, since you may not be able to zone out easily if you need to change the difficulty setting!''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=86495;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Mr. Coinbender,\\n\\nYour payment''''s been arranged, but I had to leave it off shore so the local orcs wouldn''''t confiscate the goods.\\n\\nI''''ve put out some buoys to help you find it. Best of luck, pal.\\n\\nRegards,\\nGazrix Gearlock''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=86893;
