UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Oh, did I forget to mention that your payment is on the bottom of the ocean?  Maybe you''''ll think about that next time you try to double-cross the Cartel.\\n\\nJust keep swimming down, though. I''''m sure you''''ll find it, chump.\\n\\n- GG''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=86896;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''The last I remember, I was enjoying a book under a tree somewhere nearby. I''''m not sure quite where, though.\\n\\nI seem to recall large stones... and for some reason a painting of a death''''s-head... but that is all.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=86930;
