UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Commander, check this thing out. We found an Iron Star and Thaelin over there has been helping me get it fully operational.\\n\\nI think it''''s ready for action, if you want to give it a test roll.\\n\\nKhadgar and the others said they''''d meet you at the entrance to the harbor. Maybe run over any Iron Horde you encounter along the way for kicks.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=88734;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Cheers, commander. We found this Iron Star here just waitin'''' to be repaired, and Gazlowe over there has been helpin'''' me fix it up.\\n\\nIt should be ready for action when you are.\\n\\nKhadgar said he''''d meet ya down by the harbor with the others. I''''m a wee bit jealous that ya get to roll over some Iron Horde in this thing.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=88736;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''This world don''''t give us nothing, $n. It be our lot to suffer... and our duty to fight back.$b$b\\nThis Horde be our family! We don''''t always see eye-to-eye. We come to blows before. But when we work together - ah - there''''s nothing this Horde can''''t do.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=88757;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''This unusual arakkoa seems to have suffered mortal wounds from some sort of powerful dark magic.\\n\\nWhatever caused these wounds, however, is nowhere to be seen.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=88823;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Looking for a way to impress your friends? Maybe catch the eye of a lass you bumped into at the inn? Well, you''''re in luck, my friend. Feast your eyes on Bil Sparktonic''''s fantastical incantations!\\n\\nFor a low, low price, you too can enchant the world and make it glow! \\n\\nMy assistant, Bob, can also help you with recipes for the latest and greatest enchantments from Draenor!''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=88925;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Welcome to Sparktonic''''s Enchantments, offering the lowest prices on enchanting in Stormshield.\\n\\nCare to browse our recipes?''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=88930;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''Stare into the darkness of your demise.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=89193;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''A model with skill such as mine does not come without dedication.  \\n\\nI have spent a lifetime perfecting my signature poses.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=89198;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''In my days with the rangari, I have learned many nuances of skinning the varied beasts of Draenor.\\n\\nNow that I am in Stormshield, however, I find it is much more enjoyable to pass these teachings onto others, than to toil in the fields with the skinning knife.\\n\\nWouldn''''t you agree?''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=89238;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''That Swann may not have been born a dwarf, but the heat of the forge runs through her veins. \\n\\nI could not ask for a finer apprentice.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=89239;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''It is good that you have come to Ashran, $C. You will likely be needed in the days to come.\\n\\nThe artifacts found on this island from the ancient ogre kingdom may be the determining factor in our battle against the Iron Horde. Unfortunately, the Horde has decided that they wish to take this knowledge for their own, in spite of our truce.\\n\\nWe must not let the Horde impede our efforts against our foe here on Draenor. Take the battle to them and pry the artifacts from their dead hands if you must!\\n\\nFor the Alliance!''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=89245;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Our people appreciate the aid you have lent us against the Adherents of Rukhmar. \\n\\nWe will not forget your generosity.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=89246;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''The appearance of the Order of the Awakened vexes many of the Outcasts. Though they claim their intentions are pure, their kind has wronged us so many times before.\\n\\nWe hope they are true to their words, but for now we will wait and see.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=89247;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''I am not a fighter myself, but I feel like even the most battle-minded of us should step away from time to time to enjoy some peace and quiet.\\n\\nFor me, there''''s no better way to do so then with a fishing rod in your hand and the gentle sounds of the ocean. \\n\\nWhat do you think, $C?''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=89248;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''I sell designs for the techniques used to harness the power of Draenor''''s crystals. \\n\\nIf you are skilled enough, you may benefit greatly from this knowledge.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=89361;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''I have for sale a collection of plans for the most wondrous creations of your imagination!\\n\\nCare to take a look?''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=89362;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Do you have what it takes to shape the metals of Draenor to your bidding? \\n\\nIf you do, then my plans may be of use to you.''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=89363;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''I am quite busy, as you can no doubt see. \\n\\nAre you going to buy something?''', `VerifiedBuild`=21154 WHERE `ID`=89365;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''You need to talk to Audrey Burnhep in Stormwind City!  Any guard there should be able to give you directions to find her.\\n\\nYou will find a portal to Stormwind inside the Mage Tower.  Good luck!''' WHERE `ID`=89371;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Some think it strange, but I find the rhythmic sound of goblin machinery to be quite relaxing. \\n\\nThe smell, however, I could do without.''' WHERE `ID`=89959;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''The herbs and fungus found on Draenor can be used to concoct all manner of pestilence. \\n\\nI believe our next plague will be the best yet!''' WHERE `ID`=90146;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''With my recipes, you can transform the reagents of Draenor into concoctions with the power to bestow or destroy life as you see fit.\\n\\nThat is, of course, if you possess the proper skill to wield them.''' WHERE `ID`=90153;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Many beasts of Draenor have hides as resilient as the toughest kodo. \\n\\nWith the proper skill, I can show you how to work these hides into fine armors.''' WHERE `ID`=90165;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''You look like you could use an updated wardrobe.  \\n\\nLuckily for you, I may just be able to teach you how to make some of the finest tailored garments in Draenor.\\n\\nCare to take a look at my patterns?''' WHERE `ID`=90172;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''The draenei crystalsmiths closely guard the secrets to harnessing the latent power of the gems of Draenor. \\n\\nI, however, have managed to access these secrets and can share them with a talented jewelcrafter.\\n\\nFor a price, of course.''' WHERE `ID`=90173;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''I see ya wishin'''' to enhance ya gear with da powah of da voodoo. \\n\\nGed''''kah can be of service, mon.''' WHERE `ID`=90174;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''Da right words have da powah of da strongest voodoo. \\n\\nDem dat keep da words, dey know real powah!''' WHERE `ID`=90175;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''These Iron Horde guys think they know how to make machines. \\n\\nJust wait until they see what a goblin can do once we get our hands on their tech!''' WHERE `ID`=90176;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''With the Alliance making themselves a threat again on Ashran, the demand for quality weapons and armor is higher than ever!\\n\\nDo you smell profit?''' WHERE `ID`=90177;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''You be free to house any of ya animals here wit'''' da raptas. We will be keepin dem well fed. \\n\\nYa animals, of course. What did ya think I meant?''' WHERE `ID`=90182;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''The reagents of Draenor are as wondrous as they are mysterious.\\n\\nFor a price, I can teach you to harness their potential.''' WHERE `ID`=90186;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''If this artifact that Harrison is seeking is as powerful as he seems to think, I hope it remains undiscovered.\\n\\nRegardless of intentions, the wielding of great power often comes with drastic consequences.''' WHERE `ID`=90340;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Many adventurers have come to Ashran of late. Some seek their own personal fortune, while others come to aid the Alliance in their plight against the Horde.\\n\\nWhat adventure do you seek here, friend?''' WHERE `ID`=90386;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Da Alliance think dey so smart. Dey hidin'''' behind dis truce of deirs, meanwhile dey searchin'''' dis island high and low for a powerful weapon, but dey no askin'''' for our help.\\n\\nSure, dey say da weapon is ta be used against da Iron Horde, but what is ta stop dem from turnin'''' it on us once we off dis world?\\n\\nI say we take da weapon, and we be showin'''' dem who has da powah - on dis world as well as ours.\\n\\nFor da Horde!''' WHERE `ID`=90535;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''I''''m sorry $Gladdie:lass;, but I can''''t give you access to the vault.\\n\\nThis is where Dr Jones is keepin'''' his artifacts secure. Even though the Explorer''''s League is allowing adventurers to store their gear in the extra space, the vault stays off limits.''' WHERE `ID`=90706;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Zarg like kitties. Zarg train his little kitties to be cute little warriors. \\n\\nWhat? Why you look at me like that? \\n\\nYou got something against kitties?''' WHERE `ID`=90794;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''You need talk to Varzok in Orgrimmar!  Any guard there should be able to give directions to him.\\n\\nDa portal to Orgrimmar inside shaman hut.  Good luck!''' WHERE `ID`=90795;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''After the toll taken from our assault on the Dark Portal, much of our remaining forces came to regroup here in Ashran. It is unfortunate that hostilities with the Alliance came shortly after.\\n\\nDo you seek refuge here, as well, or do you wish to stoke the flames of battle further?''' WHERE `ID`=90810;
