UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Togg, next time you use da forge, remember to hammer da blade while it still nice and hot. \\n\\nIf you put da blade in da water before you hammer it, it just gonna break again.''' WHERE `ID`=92706;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''True wisdom can only be reached when we focus as one.\\n\\nIt is then that the path will be opened.''' WHERE `ID`=92746;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''This appears to be the altar the ogres use to place offerings for the ancient rylaks. The bones of previous meals lay scattered about.\\n\\nIf you can find a proper offering, perhaps you could lure one of the rylaks down. \\n\\nThe bones may provide some clue as to what they would eat...''' WHERE `ID`=92754;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''<As you approach the ravager, a high-pitched, chittering voice echoes in your mind.>\\n\\nYou drink the seeing juice, and now you speak! You must be friend of the skull-head. \\n\\nYou here to take skulls too?''' WHERE `ID`=92799;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''$B***** RULES OF THE GAME *****\\n$B$GHe:She; who starts the game will be the|cFF990000 Seeker|r and gain the ability to|cFF2959D3 Tag|r party members. All other party members will gain the ability to|cFF2959D3 Hide|r.\\n$BThe |cFF990000 Seeker|r has 60 seconds from the time the game begins to find and|cFF2959D3 Tag|r a party member.\\n$BHidden party members will be revealed if they move OR if the|cFF990000 Seeker|r draws near. Players who can reach home base without being|cFF2959D3 Tagged|r win!''' WHERE `ID`=93090;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Switching the building will cost 500 gold.\\n\\nAre you sure?''', `FemaleText`='''Switching the building will cost 500 gold.\\n\\nAre you sure?''' WHERE `ID`=93339;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Oh, hello there.  I don''''t get many visitors up here.\\n\\nYou may not know this, but I''''m the author of Tome of the Clear Mind.  It''''s a best seller, for sure, but I came up here for inspiration on something less technical.''' WHERE `ID`=93525;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''In this cave, chieftains of the Bleeding Hollow perform a ritual to see glimpses of the future, and their own death. The other chieftains... they blindly follow Kilrogg... but not us. Grommash was worthy, Gul''''dan...\\n\\nWe have felt disturbances deep in Draenor. We believe Gul''''dan means to do great harm to Draenor, and our tribe will suffer greatly for it.''' WHERE `ID`=93550;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''My name is Fen Tao, and I am from Pandaria.  I have spent many days traveling to these lands.  Why you ask?\\n\\nWe are a family of helpful people, and you look like someone that could use some help.  Just let me know how I can be of service to you.''' WHERE `ID`=93596;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Oh, I''''ve had better nights... I was working on a beautiful enchantment for months and months but no one got to see it!\\n\\nHey, would YOU like to see it?''' WHERE `ID`=93600;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Need some help with the shopping list?\\n\\nBass Blaster''''s easy. The Ogres love loud music to go with their fights at the Ring of Blood. The spectators aren''''t there to fight. Just take it from them!\\n\\nI seem to remember a working Laz-tron down at Pinchwhistle Point, from a gig I played there once.\\n\\nWe''''ll never find a real Phonic Amplifier, so just rip a big hunk of metal off of one of those Arakkoa sun constructs. That''''ll do fine.\\n\\nAs for the capacitor, you''''ll probably need to break open an Iron Horde shredder. Seems like your kind of work.\\n\\nOh, and the kind of wood I need has to be seriously ancient, so Everbloom Wilds is probably your best bet in Draenor.''', `FemaleText`='''Need some help with the shopping list?\\n\\nBass Blaster''''s easy. The Ogres love loud music to go with their fights at the Ring of Blood. The spectators aren''''t there to fight. Just take it from them!\\n\\nI seem to remember a working Laz-tron down at Pinchwhistle Point, from a gig I played there once.\\n\\nWe''''ll never find a real Phonic Amplifier, so just rip a big hunk of metal off of one of those Arakkoa sun constructs. That''''ll do fine.\\n\\nAs for the capacitor, you''''ll probably need to break open an Iron Horde shredder. Seems like your kind of work.\\n\\nOh, and the kind of wood I need has to be seriously ancient, so Everbloom Wilds is probably your best bet in Draenor.''' WHERE `ID`=93686;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''You sure do like to talk about air! Bit of a one-trick subject, though. \\n\\nBoring, is what I''''m saying.''' WHERE `ID`=93728;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''A song? Well, there''''s nothing that goes better with lumberjacking than singing, that''''s for sure!  \\n\\nWhat kind of song are you looking for?''' WHERE `ID`=93729;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Ha, yes! The wilderness is both serene and wild, the perfect subject of a song.\\n\\nI happen to have one of the old lumberjack''''s songs written down here. Would you like a copy?''' WHERE `ID`=93735;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Need some help with the shopping list?\\n\\nI hate to encourage theft, but the Ogres partying at the Ring of Blood love their Bass Blaster. I doubt they''''ll be in a fighting mood, but don''''t stick around after you swipe it from them.\\n\\nI had a Laz-tron Disc Reader stolen from me a few weeks ago, and I couldn''''t get the Goblin smell out of my bunk for a week. Check Pinchwhistle Point.\\n\\nPhonic Amplifiers are tough to find. A piece of metal from an Arakkoa construct might be enough.\\n\\nIf you''''re up to sticking it to some Iron Horde, their shredders in Talador usually have the sort of capacitor I need.\\n\\nAnd for the finishing touch, wood from the ancients in Gorgrond, if the Commandojacks have spared any.''', `FemaleText`='''Need some help with the shopping list?\\n\\nI hate to encourage theft, but the Ogres partying at the Ring of Blood love their Bass Blaster. I doubt they''''ll be in a fighting mood, but don''''t stick around after you swipe it from them.\\n\\nI had a Laz-tron Disc Reader stolen from me a few weeks ago, and I couldn''''t get the Goblin smell out of my bunk for a week. Check Pinchwhistle Point.\\n\\nPhonic Amplifiers are tough to find. A piece of metal from an Arakkoa construct might be enough.\\n\\nIf you''''re up to sticking it to some Iron Horde, their shredders in Talador usually have the sort of capacitor I need.\\n\\nAnd for the finishing touch, wood from the ancients in Gorgrond, if the Commandojacks have spared any.''' WHERE `ID`=93780;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Our siege began the moment you took the boats. It looked like it would be a long battle until a large part of their forces departed suddenly, most likely when you attacked from the east.$b$b\\nThen we hit them with everything. Thaelin brought in a massive powered ram and the gates fell quickly. Then we ran into this new foe... the fel orcs. They press us sorely and we can make no headway. I hope you are having better luck in the east.''' WHERE `ID`=94058;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''The Black Candle... I know not where Gul''''dan found this. It never burns down and exudes a corruptive smoke as it lights everything with an unholy glint.\\n\\nMy fingers still feel oily from when I touched it.''' WHERE `ID`=94336;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''The Tome was stolen from the Imperator Mar''''gok himself, though he blames the Frostwolf clan for the theft. It is more arcane in nature but is still usable by warlocks.\\n\\nThe enchantments from this tome are a core component to the barrier spell. Fear not, I can dispel it though it may cost me dearly.''' WHERE `ID`=94338;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''It is a true mystery. Gul''''dan went through great lengths to get this dagger. He says it was quite the adventure. \\n\\nHe made sure I knew it was the most important part of the spell. Truth be told, when I held it I felt nothing. I''''m not entirely sure it did anything at all, but we should get it just in case. Gul''''dan wouldn''''t have given it to me otherwise... right?''' WHERE `ID`=94340;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Jus to da southeast lies Fang''''rila. You be bringing friends wit ya, de Blackfang saberon are de most powerful tribe I ever seen. \\n\\nYou bring back da claws and mebbe I have some tings for ya...''' WHERE `ID`=94791;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Summa dem kitties been around a while. They only come out when ya challenge dem.\\n\\nGo kill summa dem cats.\\n\\nI take ya claws and make a challenge totem. Take it to da Fang''''rila arena and place it. It be sure to anger one of dem really big ones. Make sure ya bring friends, them kitties be no joke!''' WHERE `ID`=94793;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Are you sure you want to buy th''''gear I''''ve got for sale? Crunchpaw has th'''' best stuff these days.\\n\\nB''''tween the two of us, I heard she didn''''t get her nickname from fightin'''' the Horde.\\n\\nDon''''t tell her I said that.\\n\\nActually, I''''d prefer y''''din''''t even mention that we spoke. I''''m not on her good side right now.''' WHERE `ID`=95562;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Greetings, and thank you for helping to test patch 6.2!\\n\\nI can teleport you directly into Hellfire Citadel or Tanaan Jungle. This is just a teleport, not a match-making service, so I hope you have a party ready to tackle the challenges waiting inside. If not, you might want to check out our new Group Finder feature to find some allies.\\n\\nMake sure you have selected the difficulty you want to test before teleporting, since you may not be able to zone out easily if you need to change the difficulty setting!''' WHERE `ID`=96300;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''The differences that have set the Arakkoa apart for years seem so trivial today. We have squandered the might of our people on fear and mistrust of one another when we should have been looking beyond the safety of Skyreach. There is nothing to be done about the past, but know that there are some who wish for our people to be more than a footnote to what Gul''''dan has wrought.\\n\\nI will help you, $c. We must all help one another now, or this world is doomed.''' WHERE `ID`=96939;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''The drake under you is mortally wounded and about to fall! Move to another drake, quickly!\\n\\n|TInterface\\\\Icons\\\\inv_misc_hook_01.blp:32|t''' WHERE `ID`=50183;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''If you can''''t fight at range, use your Jump Drakes! ability:\\n\\n|TInterface\\\\Icons\\\\ability_vehicle_launchplayer.blp:64|t''', `FemaleText`='''If you can''''t fight at range, use your Jump Drakes! ability:\\n\\n|TInterface\\\\Icons\\\\ability_vehicle_launchplayer.blp:64|t''' WHERE `ID`=50338;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Weary of one of your demonic charges? Hoping for one with a more pleasing name?\\n\\nFor a price, I can assist you in the obliteration of a current minion so that you may summon an entirely new one...''', `FemaleText`='''Weary of one of your demonic charges? Hoping for one with a more pleasing name?\\n\\nFor a price, I can assist you in the obliteration of a current minion so that you may summon an entirely new one...''' WHERE `ID`=50695;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''You seek the newly-arrived Highborne? So be it.\\n\\nYou''''ll find them in the western wing of the Temple of the Moon. There may be one of them at the Howling Oak, as well.''', `FemaleText`='''You seek the newly-arrived Highborne? So be it.\\n\\nYou''''ll find them in the western wing of the Temple of the Moon. There may be one of them at the Howling Oak, as well.''' WHERE `ID`=50741;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''\\nWeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee!''' WHERE `ID`=50779;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Ye don'''' want ta'''' be goin up dis'''' way, mon.  Da spirits be restless.\\n\\nMebbe if ye'''' know a ting or two about ancient artifacts, ye can fin'''' a way to put dem to rest.''' WHERE `ID`=51263;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''I can teach the art of cooking.\\n\\nAre you looking to learn?''', `FemaleText`='''I can teach the art of cooking.\\n\\nAre you looking to learn?''' WHERE `ID`=51896;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''It is not the fighters I watch; that is the Combat Masters'''' task.\\n\\nMy concern is for the two neophytes whose duty it is to heal them. So far, my students are doing well.''' WHERE `ID`=51905;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Oh, aye. I took the wee rotter''''s candle.\\n\\nNow, what did ye need?''' WHERE `ID`=51906;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''I consider it a great honor to assist the Lady Proudmoore in her research. She''''s the most powerful human mage upon Azeroth, you know!\\n\\nNow, was there something I might help you with?''' WHERE `ID`=51946;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='''Were this tower to boast TWICE as many tomes, it would still not be enough for me. My collecting and copying shall never be done.\\n\\nSo. You have need of my assistance?''' WHERE `ID`=51948;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''You mean to say there is a warlock? Here, in goodly Theramore?!\\n\\nOh, my. Someone must inform Lady Proudmoore immediately!\\n\\n...heh.''' WHERE `ID`=51955;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='''Please, lower your voice. It isn''''t wise to remind Lady Proudmoore of the sorts of things we study.\\n\\nNow, shall we speak of TRUE power...?''' WHERE `ID`=51957;
